ygData.messageBody:
Congrats!!!!!!!

The Sister Island should be a great place for the weddng. I will try to be
there, if I can stay awake (am on Eastern Time).

Now the question is, where have you two registered for gifts? Jade the
Jeweler? Leather and Hide? :)

Are you planning on announcing this on any of the poplular EQ web sites? It
wouldn't be the first same-sex wedding you know.

If anyone needs an escort for lower level characters from far away lands,
let me know and I'll provide protection to get you to the wedding.

Dedric, gnome necromancer, lvl 21 on Brell
